This is a forum I've followed for long time now.
For the 1st time I feel there's an actual collaboration I can provide my community with.
In Mexico there are available motorcycles in the 300cc class from Vento which are affordable and reliable.
Plenty of maintenance, repairing and/or upgradind tips have been released in FB.
I'll compile them all together in a single thread for eveyone interested to be able to find the information easily.

All the best
